    "Bard's response to drawing prompts.www.ijacsa.thesai.org It should be noted that Fig. 6 showcases the result of a very specific prompt with weight distribution that is as follows: \"breathtaking, mysterious, fantasy, magical, (female robot:1.5) (creating a machine with hands), surrealism, hyper-realistic, colors and shapes, highly detailed, realism pushed to extreme, fine texture, 8k, ultra-detailed, (vivid swirling smoke, thick smoke:1.4), fluid, fire, cinematic, (intricate details:1.5), (vibrant colors:1.4), flash explosion, (colorful powder explosion), (billowing hair:1.5) \"((magical enchantment on hands))\" \"((creates a machine from hands towards viewer))\"\".",
    "The LLM allows for incredibly detailed instructions that can be followed, such instructions are unavailable for the other tested tools currently.",
    "Fig. 5, 7 and 8 display the limitations of the most popular models.",
